{"tid":2048376,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"上星期飲左Presha Fruit，覺得自己就黎肚痛","createTime":"2020-06-02T18:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T17:55:09.000Z","uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0804f92b150ccea3792d0768e7115e826592817","tid":2048376,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T18:31:25.000Z","msg":"Presha Fruit蘋果汁「棒曲霉素」超標 或引致胃腸不適等徵狀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryxJY6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryxJY6F.jpg&h=82a7dc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食安中心今日（2日）公布，一個澳洲進口Presha Fruit瓶裝果汁飲品樣本受霉菌毒素「棒曲霉素」污染，有關進口商／分銷商已按中心指令將受影響批次的產品停售及下架，並展開回收。<br />\n<br />\n中心發言人表示，早前公布一個瓶裝蘋果汁飲品樣本受棒曲霉素污染，於跟進調查時再從巿面抽取同一品牌的另一款瓶裝果汁飲品樣本進行檢測，檢測結果發現樣本含十億分之一百二十的棒曲霉素，超出中心採用的行動水平十億分之五十。中心採用的行動水平與食品法典委員會關於蘋果汁內的棒曲霉素標準一樣。"},{"pid":"d899644b55ab180b16542d35759124ff69b67a70","tid":2048376,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T18:33:08.000Z","msg":"唔想死&hellip;"},{"pid":"547bcd336dedbd8dc26e8579cb67301d6099562f","tid":2048376,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d899644b55ab180b16542d35759124ff69b67a70","tid":2048376,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T18:33:08.000Z","msg":"唔想死&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T21:16:44.000Z","msg":"橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70fc505673fb92c15efd5c83eeac757b510ce80","tid":2048376,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:18:52.000Z","msg":"R.A.P"},{"pid":"21fdb37eec73c0e0b1b0c813c35d541416c91aae","tid":2048376,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"547bcd336dedbd8dc26e8579cb67301d6099562f","tid":2048376,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d899644b55ab180b16542d35759124ff69b67a70","tid":2048376,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T18:33:08.00